Package de.dezibel.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Commentable
    This interface must be implemented by all classes that can be commented.
    Lockable
    Interface which stores functionality to lock and unlock contents which implement it.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Album
    This class represents an Album.
    Application
    This class represents the application from an artist for a label and vice versa.
    Comment
    This class represents the comments users can post to Media, Albums etc.
    Database
    This singleton class represents the Database.
    Genre
    This class represents a genre which can be used to classify the Medium objects.
    Label
    This class represents a Label.
    Medium
    Stores information about a music file, which can be uploaded, played, deleted and locked by fitting users.
    News
    This class represents news.
    Playlist
    This class represents a playlist, which can be created by a creator.
    Rating
    This class represents a rating of a mediaobject made by a user.
    User
    Stores personal-, login- and role-informations about the user.
